{
  "stem": "17001.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 249.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To tell you the honest truth, I-- I really don't know if it was a week or if it was four days or three days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing that I had forget to mention, that all those months that we were in Auschwitz, we cried so much that our eyes just dried up.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It got to the point when no tears were coming out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That we used up all our tears.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the tears that we had shed while we were in Auschwitz, a whole river could form.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of things that I forget to mention, that what was going on during the night, that how the people were crying and singing and all that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But once we were leaving and we were at the gate and I was at the front, I was thinking there is such a thing that we will walk out of here, and not the way the-- Lola, the block-- the Lageralteste had said that we would go through the smoke.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I said, then it must be a miracle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After all this hiding of the selection, going from one barrack to the next, and then trying to finagle here, finagle there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I said, maybe God is really good to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we start go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were supposed to be 550 girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But by the time they get wind of it, that we are going, there was at least 15,000.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they cut it down, and I was happy I was at the front of the line, that I wasn't cut down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As we were marched and we were going, we were passing between the same two lager, the men's lager and the [GERMAN], as we were both in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we are going.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
